Project Scenario:
Create a straightforward "Task Manager" application, allowing users to add, mark completion, and
remove tasks effortlessly.
Implementation Details:
HTML Structure:
Design a user-friendly interface with an input field for adding tasks and a list for displaying them.
CSS Styling:
Apply clean and intuitive styling to enhance the overall appearance of the application.
JavaScript Functionality:
Implement core functionality such as adding tasks, marking them as complete, and removing tasks.
Leverage local storage to retain tasks even after a page refresh.
Responsiveness:
Prioritize responsiveness to guarantee a seamless user experience across various devices.
Optional Features:
Integrate additional elements, such as a date/time picker for task deadlines or a filter for completed
and active tasks, based on personal preferences.